  <div class="sb"><div class="v c1">0</div><div class="l">Blood Vessels in<br>Articular Cartilage</div></div>
  <div class="sb"><div class="v c2">36</div><div class="l">Preclinical BPC-157<br>Studies (to 2024)</div></div>
  <div class="sb"><div class="v c3">60%</div><div class="l">Of OA Patients<br>Are Over 60</div></div>
